import './App.css';
import Navbar from "./navbar"

function App() {
  let Component 
  switch (window.location.pathname){
    case "/":
      Component = App
      break
      case "/products":
        Component = Products
        break
        case "/contact-us":
          Component = Contact
          break
  }
  return <>
  <Navbar />
  <Component />
  </>
    
}

export default App;
